lead_paragraph: Freestyle queen Katie Ledecky swam the fastest women's 400 meters of the year on Sunday while the U.S. men's team, minus Michael Phelps for now, showed the Australians they mean business in the 4x100 relay.

headline.main: Swimming: Ledecky Lights Up Pool With Phelps Yet to Come
